<section id="howtojoin" class="howtojoin">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>How to join?</h1>
        <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
            <p class="lead"><a href="#schedule" class=""><i class="fa fa-flag-o fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i>&nbsp;Registration deadline is extended until 31st August!</a></p>
        </div>
        <h3><p class="text-warning"><i class="fa fa-book fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i>&nbsp;Step by Step Guide <small>- Registration Workflow- </small></h3>
        <div class="row featurette">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <div class="panel-group" id="accordion-join" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
                    <div class="panel panel-success">
                        <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingOne">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-join" href="#stepOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="stepOne">
                                    STEP 1. Getting the invitation from TJ-SIF2016 SECRETARIAT
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="stepOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOne">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>TJ-SIF2016 SECRETARIAT has already sent the invitations to both of English & computer contact persons at each PCSH Schools. <u>If you are a contact person in PCSHS and have not got the invitation yet, please ask SECRETARIAT for it immediately.</u></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel panel-success">
                        <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingTwo">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-join" href="#stepTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="stepTwo">
                                    STEP 2. Contact Person Registration
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="stepTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingTwo">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>Contact persons  in PCSHS <strong>MUST</strong> register first.</p>
                                <p>When register your information, choose account type:</p>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                    <li>A. English contact person: <mark>“Contact person”</mark>.</li>
                                    <li>B. Computer contact person who…
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>B-1. takes care student project: <mark>“Participant”</mark></li>
                                            <li>B-2. doesn’t care student project: <mark>“Contact person”</mark></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel panel-success">
                        <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingThree">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-join" href="#stepThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="stepThree">
                                    STEP 3. Sending the Invitations
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="stepThree" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThree">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>Contact persons in PCSHS send the invitation to another contact person and related teachers. When contact person login, you can see the link <strong>"Invitation"</strong> on the top-right in the navigation menu. Click <strong>"Invitation"</strong>, enter user name which is used only in the invitation mail and email address twice, then click <button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Send invitation</button> to send the invitation.</p>
                                <p>Contact person should send the invitation to:</p>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                    <li>A. English contact person: contact person in SSH in Japan</li>
                                    <li>B. Computer contact person: contact person in sister school in Thailand</li>
                                    <li>C. Both of contact person: teachers in your school</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel panel-success">
                        <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingFour">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-join" href="#stepFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="stepFour">
                                    STEP 4. Teachers Registration
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="stepFour" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingFour">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>When you get the invitation mail from contact person in your school, click the link in the mail then register your personal information.</p>
                                <p>When register your information, choose account type as follows.<br>Teacher who…</p>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                    <li>A. takes care student project: <mark>“Participant”</mark></li>
                                    <li>B. doesn’t care student project but who
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>B-1. is going to TJ-SIF2016: <mark>“Operation staff”</mark></li>
                                            <li>B-2. is not going to TJ-SIF2016: <mark>“Observation”</mark></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                    <blockquote>
                                        <p><strong>Note:</strong> Every invitation link is <strong>unique</strong> so that you can not use the link the other’s. You have not got the invitation yet, please ask contact person in your school.</p>
                                    </blockquote>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel panel-success">
                        <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingFive">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-join" href="#stepFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="stepFive">
                                    STEP 5. Inviting Students
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="stepFive" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingFive">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>Teachers who register their information with <mark>“Participant”</mark> --- this means teacher will support student project --- send the invitations to the students.</p>
                                <p>How to send the invitation is the same as contact person. Please see <em>"STEP3. Sending the Invitatioin"</em></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel panel-success">
                        <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingSix">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-join" href="#stepSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="stepSix">
                                    STEP 6. Projects Registering
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="stepSix" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingSix">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>Teachers who register their information with <mark>“Participant”</mark> should create some student project from <strong>“informations > projects”</strong> on the navigation menu on the top, then click <button type="button" class="btn btn-default">New</button> to create project.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" src="{{ asset('/images/featurette/IMG_03_07_500.jpg') }}" alt="About picture">
            </div>
            {{ render(controller('AppBundle:Statistics:defaultpage')) }}
        </div><!-- /.row featurette -->
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
    </div><!-- /.container -->
</section><!-- /about -->
